Highly pathogenic avian influenza (HPAI) virus continues to sweep across the continent. The number of birds being euthanized or dying from this virus is in the many millions. Clearly, this is impacting the availability of poultry products and resulting in increasing prices on many levels. Wild birds are also being affected.

It is paramount to protect your birds, including our wildlife birds. If you own birds -- even as a small operator -- biosecurity is a very high priority. Live it, breathe it, practice it. - Mod.TG]
